{"tid":1984290,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"個件sigma罵得好啱，你班廢柴淨係識用埋啲下三流手段，唔會噉明刀明槍","createTime":"2020-04-22T11:04:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T15:42:53.000Z","uid":38539,"like":28,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"efeb088f65f3488a5507c3142043fa931c65132f","tid":1984290,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"雖然我唔太知發生咩事，咁啱見到有人開帖話佢出片講俾人捧殺，入咗去望幾眼，<br />\n但是其是，非其非，你唔鍾意人一係就據理力爭，有咩申訴一五一十講清楚，<br />\n再絕啲咪約人出去隻揪，而唔係走去用埋哂啲賤招，係連登狂開廢帖捧殺人，<br />\n成隻縮頭烏龜，人哋在明，你就在暗，根本就係一場不公平的戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於此，近日連登部份會員為sigma哥仔帶嚟各種不便，<br />\n我正式代表連登一眾會員向sigma致歉，<br />\n我個份人好均真，並唔會因為出自同一門派就互相包庇，<br />\n你哋整臭哂成個連登個朵，真正的連登人會以你哋為恥！"},{"pid":"a816d60abaf9384c48faf8908076e1cb721293b9","tid":1984290,"uid":136738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:06:12.000Z","msg":"sorry sir"},{"pid":"91b65b74a4c00d8d24552dd13aea8bf9bc32c030","tid":1984290,"uid":22989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:06:14.000Z","msg":"是其是 非其非<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f0cd27792307252b3afa7c681f41d8aba49d4a2","tid":1984290,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:06:39.000Z","msg":"開POST個班都係我D手下 我代佢地道歉"},{"pid":"ac4758cd5d3bd4312b6b7c5f99cf97b17c0ff341","tid":1984290,"uid":205928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:11:51.000Z","msg":"沒錯<br />\n我地一定要好好保護恩師sigma🙏🏻"},{"pid":"69a28244f5902757fb7e1db4a4b5789ac5848389","tid":1984290,"uid":74465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"愚台已經變左做色麻台"},{"pid":"83e35bd1e7b7cb5ff9ab69511b83750dd1c8173d","tid":1984290,"uid":136738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69a28244f5902757fb7e1db4a4b5789ac5848389","tid":1984290,"uid":74465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11:14:57.000Z","msg":"愚台已經變左做色麻台"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T11